<Author>PaulHogle
<Content>Fantastic Experience! My family (three teenage daughters and my wife and I) stayed in the Hotel Brandies for 4 nights. It was a perfect delight. The front desk staff is cordial and accomodating; the breakfast is a nice feature and has an ample variety; the rooms are clean, with tall ceilings, comfortable beds. The rooms in the rear of the Hotel overlook a lovely courtyard. Hotel Brandiess is an uncomplicated, celan, safe, and pleasant exeperience.Outside the front door, it is fewer than 20 steps to the Kaiserdam station on the U2 subway line; the S train is a little more than a block away.One block north of the Hotel is a grocery store along with several very friendly restaurants.When next in Berlin with the family, we will certainly return to Hotel Brandies!! 
